msgid ""
"Cache cleared. Next scan will fetch fresh checksums from WordPress.org."
msgstr ""
"Caché eliminada. El próximo análisis obtendrá checksums nuevos de "
"WordPress.org."

msgid ""
"Compares every WordPress core file against the official MD5 checksums "
"published by WordPress.org. Detects files that have been modified, are "
"missing or have been unexpectedly added to wp-admin/ or wp-includes/. It "
"does NOT scan plugins, themes or uploads."
msgstr ""
"Compara cada archivo del núcleo de WordPress con los checksums MD5 oficiales"
" publicados por WordPress.org. Detecta archivos modificados, que faltan o "
"que se han añadido inesperadamente a wp-admin/ o wp-includes/. NO analiza "
"plugins, temas ni uploads."

msgid ""
"Checksums are fetched from the WordPress.org API and cached locally for 24 "
"hours. Only WordPress Core files are verified — wp-content/ is intentionally"
" excluded. Modified files are not automatically restored; always review "
"changes before taking action."
msgstr ""
"Los checksums se obtienen de la API de WordPress.org y se guardan en caché "
"localmente durante 24 horas. Solo se verifican los archivos del núcleo de "
"WordPress — wp-content/ se excluye intencionadamente. Los archivos "
"modificados no se restauran automáticamente; revise siempre los cambios "
"antes de actuar."

